You may not remove or alter attribution notices.

3. Source Availability & Network Use (AGPL‑style requirement)
If you Distribute a Covered Work in any form, you must provide the complete corresponding source code under this License, including build and installation instructions, either (a) with the distribution, or (b) via a durable network location offered at no charge.
If you enable others to interact with a Covered Work via Network Use, you must ensure that each user can immediately obtain the complete corresponding source code of the version running, under this same License, at no charge.

